183
00:27:57,604 --> 00:27:58,944
- Ah!
- (NEIGHING)

184
00:28:01,777 --> 00:28:03,780
(MOANING)

185
00:28:06,228 --> 00:28:09,079
He's going for his gun!

186
00:28:09,256 --> 00:28:11,762
Let's go! Let's go!

187
00:28:16,796 --> 00:28:20,831
Oh, Ace. Oh, Ace. Ah...

188
00:28:22,249 --> 00:28:24,267
Oh, no...

189
00:28:27,288 --> 00:28:30,711
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry. (SIGHING)

190
00:28:36,330 --> 00:28:38,615
I'm so sorry, pal.

